                                 <dim unit="leaf">8</dim>
                                 <locus from="17r" to="24v"/>The quire structure cannot be
                                 identified due to its poor condition of the Ms. Only the structure
                                 for the following quires is more certain: 
 III(8/fols.
                                 17r-24v) </item>
                              <item xml:id="q2">
                                 <dim unit="leaf">8</dim>
                                 <locus from="25r" to="32v"/> IV(8/fols. 25r-32v) </item>
                              <item xml:id="q3">
                                 <dim unit="leaf">8</dim>
