                  <handDesc>
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Fine, careful. At the beginning, the handwriting is
                           characterized by finely shaped, slender, tall and upright letters. Later, it
                           shows some irregularities with smaller, slightly right sloping and
                           irregularly spaced letters (cp. <locus target="#44">44</locus> v<locus target="#102">102</locus>)</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red</seg>
                        <date>17th century (?)</date>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Divine names; name of the original donor (erased);
                           elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.
 A
                           few lines alternating with black lines on the incipit page; two initial
                           lines of sections and section numbers.</seg>
                     </handNote>
                     
                  </handDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus from="92va" to="92vb">f. 92va-vb</locus>
                           <desc type="GuestText">Explanation of Patriarch Mark of Alexandria on the anointment
                              (qǝbʿāt) of Christ. </desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                              ይቤ፡ አቡነ፡ ሊቀ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ ማርቆስ፡ ዘእስክንድርያ፡
                              ዘውእቱ፡ ሳምናይ፡ እም፻ወ፯፡ ዘተሠይሙ፡ እማርቆስ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ እስከአሁ፡ ሶበ፡ ተስእልናሁ፡ በእንተ፡
                              ሃይማኖት፡ ርትዕት። ብሂል፡ ቅብዓት፡ ትርጓሜሁ፡ መንግሥት፡ ነው። ክብርም፡ ነው፡ አስተቀባ፡ ማለትም፡ ነገሠ፡
                              ከበረ፡ ማለት፡ ነው፡ ነገሩ፡ ቅብዓትን፡ ለመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አትስጡ፡ የወልድ፡ ነው፡ አለ። አብ፡ ለአጽንኦ፡
                              ወልድ፡ ለተሰብኦ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ለአንጽሖ፡ በማርያም፡ አደሩ፡ ይኩነኒ፡ ...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="am"/>
                           <note> The note is written in Amharic and Gǝʿǝz. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#154rb">f. 154rb</locus>
                           <desc type="Excommunication">Excommunication against those who stole this book or other books
                              from the monastery.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                              ለዝ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ወለኵሎሙ፡ መጻሕፍት፡ ቅድሳት፡
                              ዘውስተ፡ ዛቲ፡ ምኔት፡ ወምስለ፡ ኵሉ፡ ንዋየ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ዘሠረቆሙ፡ ወፈሐቆሙ፡ ወዘትንባሎሙ፡ በኃይል፡
                              በሥልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡ በዝ፡ ዓለም፡ ወበዘይመጽእ፡ አሜን።</q>
                           
                           
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#155r">f. 155ra-rb</locus>
                           <desc type="GuestText"> <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3058RepCh338">ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki ... "I worship Thee ...".</title></desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           
                           
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1"><desc>Titles of or short notes referring to miracles of St
                           Mary are written in the upper margin of the miracle's incipit page, in
                           different hands (partly faded): <locus target="#1r">1r</locus>, 43r, 44v,
                           45v, 47r, 49r, 56r, 57r, 58r, 64r, 66v, 70v, 74v, 80r, 84r, 85v,
                           87v.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e2"><desc>Erasures: <locus target="#14ra">14ra</locus>, 34vb, 36rb,
                           38rab, 50va, 57vb, 59ra, 73ra, 88ra, 105ra.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e3"><desc> Omissions are inserted
                           interlineally: <locus target="#2rb">2rb</locus>, 20rb, 25vb, 36vb, 37rb,
                           38vb, 52va, 60vb, 63rb, 64va, 84ra, 88r).</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e4"><desc>Omitted incipit of one
                           miracle (numbered as '50') has been inserted in compressed script,
                           possibly in the main hand, on <locus target="#58ra">58ra</locus>.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e5"><desc>
                           Corrections are written over erasures: <locus target="#25ra">25ra</locus>, 36vb, 50ra, 59rb.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e6"><desc> Scribbles: <locus target="#7v">7v</locus>, 71r, 76r-77r, 92v, 93r, 94r, 98v-99r.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e7"><desc>Crude
                           drawing: <locus target="#155v">155v</locus>.</desc></item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
                  <bindingDesc>
                     <binding contemporary="partly">
                        <decoNote xml:id="b1">Two wooden boards covered with reddish-brown tooled
